                    <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #666;">Discover more about the vision and legacy of our Founding Dolls</p>
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <a href="founders-museum.html" style="display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 2rem; background: var(--color-secondary); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600;">Visit the Museum</a>
                        <a href="moments-that-made-us.html" style="display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 2rem; background: white; color: var(--color-secondary); text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; border: 2px solid var(--color-secondary);">Historical Moments</a>
                    </div>
